{{!Setup the `index.handlebars` to have the template that Handlebars 
can render onto.}}

{{! * Create a button in `index.handlebars` 
that will submit the user input into the database.}}

<h1>Burgers</h1>

<h2>It's Time For You To Eat Some Burgers!</h2>

<h2>Enter a Burger You Want To Eat Then Hit The Submit Button</h2>
<form class="create-form">

  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="ca">Burger:</label>
    <input type="text" id="ca" name="name">
  </div>

  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="sleepy">Sleepy?</label><br>
    <input type="radio" name="sleepy" value="1" checked> Sleepy!<br>
    <input type="radio" name="sleepy" value="0"> Awake
  </div>

  <button type="submit">Add Yo' Burger</button>
</form>
